{"tid":1778381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國防預算案撐港人捍衞權利","createTime":"2019-12-11T02:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T02:53:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0686d12a3a686e5ca55421409c8332b7bc92882e","tid":1778381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191211/P55BSW4PI2YVSZQ33VQKEN6S4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191211%2FP55BSW4PI2YVSZQ33VQKEN6S4I%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=2526e1bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191211%2FP55BSW4PI2YVSZQ33VQKEN6S4I%2F&h=432644c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191211/P55BSW4PI2YVSZQ33VQKEN6S4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國防預算案撐港人捍衞權利<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191211/large/1575994969_3c63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191211%2Flarge%2F1575994969_3c63.jpg&h=f417dafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國防部長埃斯珀<br />\n<br />\n美國國會議員前日宣佈就7,380億美元（約57,564億港元）國防預算法案達成協議，當中包含一系列條款應對來自中國的潛在威脅，又表明國會「明確支持」香港人捍衞權利與自治。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：上訴存變數 遮面須承擔風險<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁購中國列車巴士<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，參眾兩院軍事委員會歷經數月協商後，終於就2020財政年度國防授權法案達成共識。預料國會在年底假期前會通過法案。<br />\n<br />\n這項法案給予國防部與能源部的國家安全計劃撥款6,584億美元（約51,355億港元）；海外應急行動715億美元（約5,577億港元），以應付海外作戰；以及53億美元（約413.4億港元）作為極端天氣與天災過後的復原急難資金。<br />\n<br />\n法案也納入一系列條款應對來自中國的潛在威脅，包括要求針對中國的海外投資、中俄軍事關係提交報告；禁止使用聯邦資金向中國購買列車和巴士；「明確支持」香港居民捍衞自身權利與自治；支持改善台灣防禦能力等。<br />\n<br />\n這項法案也要求制裁購買俄製S-400防空導彈系統的土耳其，新法案禁止把洛克希德馬丁公司（Lockheed Martin Corp.）研發的F-35匿蹤戰機交付土耳其。華府也表示，S-400系統與北約（NATO）防禦系統不相容，還會威脅F-35戰機。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"78e30c5e72719e328280db666234a40657ebc7b5","tid":1778381,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"強烈要求係香港部署薩德"},{"pid":"23106152b97ecca836818fea7bc2f5b7d9f2d4ec","tid":1778381,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"sir this way 熱愛核平"},{"pid":"49a9319a220766d25a9aceb8cc12fbaae8615da9","tid":1778381,"uid":181088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78e30c5e72719e328280db666234a40657ebc7b5","tid":1778381,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"強烈要求係香港部署薩德"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:24:56.000Z","msg":"上水哥爾夫球場係個唔錯set up地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27ff409edd20b1901fc3543015a8542ae263f94","tid":1778381,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:28:57.000Z","msg":"Sir this way"},{"pid":"71e2d4e7a5a3ebcde3fc5dc64d1fe2d4595190cb","tid":1778381,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"49a9319a220766d25a9aceb8cc12fbaae8615da9","tid":1778381,"uid":181088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78e30c5e72719e328280db666234a40657ebc7b5","tid":1778381,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"強烈要求係香港部署薩德"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:24:56.000Z","msg":"上水哥爾夫球場係個唔錯set up地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:29:59.000Z","msg":"上水一個 大球場一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e709b31992b5f86cebbfdcf27c78b7143e1695e9","tid":1778381,"uid":181088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71e2d4e7a5a3ebcde3fc5dc64d1fe2d4595190cb","tid":1778381,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"